## Example Walkthrough

**`s = "cba"`**, n=3, freq={a:1,b:1,c:1}

| i | s[i] | smaller (< s[i]) | perms | contribution | freq after |
|---|------|-----------------|-------|-------------|------------|
| 0 | c | a:1+b:1=2 | 2!/(1!1!1!)=1 | 2 | {a:1,b:1,c:0} |
| 1 | b | a:1=1 | 1!/(1!1!0!)=1 | 1 | {a:1,b:0,c:0} |
| 2 | a | 0 | 0!/...=1 | 0 | {a:0,...} |

Total = 2+1+0 = **5** ✓

